    "description": "“奈何苍凉世情薄，却道最是人心恶。静待夜半魂归时，杀尽天下负情郎。”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景：</h2>《回门》是一款以传统民俗为题材的2D横版恐怖解谜游戏，以1905—1926跨越20年的时间线作为故事时代背景，呈现民国时代的民俗风貌与时代背景下主角家族的唏嘘往事。续作《过阴》已发布Steam页面。<br><br>1926年，海外学习的玉商乔氏之子乔予安留洋归来，却发现这个滨海小镇上下都笼罩着一层诡秘的疑云……风言风语的市井、含糊其辞的家人，而在寻找失踪姊妹的路上，魑魅魍魉接踵而来。<br>小镇平和的表象下到底在掩盖什么真相？这里究竟是现实，还是误入幻境？你在不同的年岁间回溯记忆。当嫁衣被蒙上血腥，几代人的宿命便再次交汇……时代的悲剧没有偶然，这是逃不开的因果！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/d175b0b09706fcdce8fd5888747a787a.avif?t=1705548535\" width=680 height=299 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><br><strong>定制个性与双重结局</strong><br>文字游戏与横版解谜游戏的个性结合，丰富的对话选项与分支剧情，主角性格将由玩家为主角量身定做。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/fdcd4b69f74e1f79abd998511b6cc533.poster.avif?t=1705548535\" width=680 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/fdcd4b69f74e1f79abd998511b6cc533.webm?t=1705548535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/fdcd4b69f74e1f79abd998511b6cc533.mp4?t=1705548535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>真人配音与跌宕剧情</strong><br>全流程主线配音，生动演绎每个角色的性格特点，多条故事线并行，呈现民国近二十年下小城镇大家族的悲喜与兴衰，悬念迭起，反转不停。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/d80745147a1b82ec888441e52ba91af9.poster.avif?t=1705548535\" width=680 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/d80745147a1b82ec888441e52ba91af9.webm?t=1705548535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/d80745147a1b82ec888441e52ba91af9.mp4?t=1705548535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>多种玩法与特色解谜</strong><br>集背包组合、追逐、潜行等多种玩法于一体，多时间线交叉解谜，时代特色浓郁的谜题设计将带领玩家亲身感受民国时期的文化习俗与风貌人情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/1d1f35d7975059809af41ea635b7f1ab.avif?t=1705548535\" width=680 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>中式恐怖与鬼怪设计</strong><br>冥婚、拜神、傀儡戏……产鬼、阴差、黄泉路、孽镜台……以民俗文化为创作蓝图，深度打造一个原汁原味的中式恐怖世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/01cd075d8072f7e0931a5696ef715209.poster.avif?t=1705548535\" width=680 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/01cd075d8072f7e0931a5696ef715209.webm?t=1705548535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218170/extras/01cd075d8072f7e0931a5696ef715209.mp4?t=1705548535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
